            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "I think there is still situation when exception on line 1045 could happen.\r\n\r\nFunction getBrowser returns empty array (lines 433-435) and if Zend_Locale is called like $locale = new Zend_Locale(Zend_Locale::BROWSER); than on line 1033 is check which probably should ensure there is always some locale returned BUT \"if (($locale === 'auto') or ($locale === null))\" second condition is not TRUE for empty array there should be \"if (($locale === 'auto') or ($locale == null))\" or  \"if (($locale === 'auto') or (empty($locale)) \" finaly on line 1038  \"$locale = key($locale);\" it makes $locale = NULL which than throws the exception.\r\n"
